  "method": [
    "Heat the oven to 400F.",
    "Mix all the components in a shallow saucepan with the marinade.",
    "Use a baking dish to put sliced vegetables.",
    "Position the veggies in and around the meat.",
    "Pour all the vegetables into the marinade and brush on the chicken.",
    "Organize the mixture equally and nestle around the sheet pan with",
    "sliced lemons.",
    "Put in the oven and bake for 30-35 minutes or until the chicken hits",
    "165 degrees and the vegetables are slightly orange.",
    "Squeeze over the fried dish with sliced lemons.",
    "Spray with olive oil with grated cheese and Kalamata."
